Class EnumControlVariables

java.lang.Object
pandemic.controls.EnumControlVariables
public class EnumControlVariables
extends java.lang.Object
Stores information, is a singielton. lockdownThreshold - how many agents need to be sick to turn on lockdown. numOfVisitsBeforeRecovering - how many visits before recovering Rest as the name suggests.
